channel.title: Can someone TeamView me? Source problems
channel.description: Im having problems with my source, and the run.bat is saying that i am missing my javac file, which im sure i have. I have tried to edit the code, but none of my attempts have been successful. I apologize, as I'm sure its something obvious but I am new to this, so please be patient as I would really like to learn the in's and out's of running a server, java, etc. If someone could use teamviewer and help me out i would really appreciate it, because like i said, I want to learn and I would like to see exactly how you all approach problems like this so I dont have to ask again, thanks.
